{"tid":568783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔准笑] 大讚利敏貞衣著「恰如其分」　邱騰華：好有 fashion sense","createTime":"2018-02-22T06:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T08:46:17.000Z","uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d20e453a357e05820a1781606d11f9d1a59cf48d","tid":568783,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:19:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fashion-07_rZlfz_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffashion-07_rZlfz_1200x0.png&d=3yCpOMOjuSI16DLlVAJxx54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dbefabd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffashion-07_rZlfz_1200x0.png&h=c931e45e\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fashion-07_rZlfz_1200x0.png</a><br />\n商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長利敏貞，日前穿上一襲「中國傳統時裝」出席記者會引來哄動。當日同場的商經局長邱騰華今天大讚利敏貞衣著恰如其分，形容對方「好有 fashion sense」，更嘉許其下屬：「有 selling point，講嘢又有point」。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前就放寬傳統媒體規管的公眾諮詢召開記者會，商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長（通訊及創意產業）利敏貞以一身「中國傳統時裝」成功「搶 fo」，成為連日來市民熱議的話題。<br />\n<br />\n當日同場出席記者會的局長邱騰華，今日參與新界鄉議局團拜時，被傳媒問及利敏貞的時裝品味。傳媒引述邱騰華指，當日是新春假期後首個工作天，利敏貞的打扮是「恰如其分」，又形容對方「好有 fashion sense」，更大讚「常秘」當日表現「有 selling point，講嘢又有point」。商經局副局長陳百里同樣力捧，形容利敏貞當日的衣著體現中國文化，是「好嘅fashion」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/fashion%E5%98%85%E5%98%A2-%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E5%88%A9%E6%95%8F%E8%B2%9E%E8%A1%A3%E8%91%97-%E6%81%B0%E5%A6%82%E5%85%B6%E5%88%86-%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF-%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%89-fashion-sense/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffashion%25E5%2598%2585%25E5%2598%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2595%258F%25E8%25B2%259E%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%2591%2597-%25E6%2581%25B0%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%2588%2586-%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%259C%2589-fashion-sense%2F&d=3yCpOMOjuSI16DLlVAJxx54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c78f1d9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffashion%25E5%2598%2585%25E5%2598%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2595%258F%25E8%25B2%259E%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%2591%2597-%25E6%2581%25B0%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%2588%2586-%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%259C%2589-fashion-sense%2F&h=0de57e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/fashion%E5%98%85%E5%98%A2-%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E5%88%A9%E6%95%8F%E8%B2%9E%E8%A1%A3%E8%91%97-%E6%81%B0%E5%A6%82%E5%85%B6%E5%88%86-%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF-%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%89-fashion-sense/</a>"},{"pid":"d2f44372b807ff7e265344f9ae7fd570bb5d4007","tid":568783,"uid":92871,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:29:53.000Z","msg":"所以話政府講野冇個可信<br />\n有fashion sense 都講得出，當人盲定on9"},{"pid":"f39db735f72f5177a793c5987c94b1cd1f6c5d0d","tid":568783,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"鏡頭前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鏡頭後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b392da1efdc49b0281906dc6b1865fdb451a38c","tid":568783,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"向y文致莖"},{"pid":"2be6cdd276d1bf6fa57e9b880962eb1d9e841b50","tid":568783,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"班下屬就慘，對住依D老姑婆上司一定好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ea58bdd0604f8643be662d3861a1833e94d256","tid":568783,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2f44372b807ff7e265344f9ae7fd570bb5d4007","tid":568783,"uid":92871,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"